  "title": "FA Technician FAT010425QPT",
  "description": "<p><strong>FA Technician FAT010425QPT</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate FA laboratory equipment to support daily lab operations and handle additional assigned tasks.</li>\n  <li>Perform general failure analysis, including electrical and physical FA, and assist in developing new analysis techniques.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable in handling chemicals using appropriate personal protective equipment (PPE).</li>\n  <li>Preferred knowledge of mobile phones, computer hardware, and components.</li>\n  <li>Test knowledge and background will be advantageous.</li>\n  <li>Strong hands-on experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Higher NITEC/Diploma in Engineering.</li>\n  <li>Basic communication skills in English, analytical skills, and proficiency in Microsoft Office.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and prioritize tasks to meet deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and strong work ethic.</li>\n  <li>Flexibility to work mid/weekend shifts and overtime if needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>· Entry Level / Candidates with no experience are welcome to apply</p>\n<p>Nationality : Singaporean/ SPR</p>\n<p>Work place : Serangoon North</p>\n<p>Type : Fresh or experienced candidate</p>\n<p>Openings :1</p>\n<p>Salary range : SGD 2500- 2550</p>\n<p>AWS , Variable Bonus : AWS eligible</p>\n<p>Attendance bonus : eligible</p>\n<p>Allowances : No</p>\n<p>Benefits : Medical Benefits eligible</p>",
